{"id": 2838, "title": "Ticket #2838: Update Globus external to 5.2.x", "description": "<blockquote>\nUpdate Globus external to 5.2.x. This is the latest version and is showing up in various linux distros.</blockquote>", "remarks": "<blockquote>\n</blockquote>", "derived_tickets": "<table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\n<tbody><tr><td align=\"right\" valign=\"top\" width=\"160\">\n<span class=\"ticket\"><a class=\"resolved\" href=\"/wiki-archive/tickets/?ticket=3110\" onclick=\"get_ticket_and_populate_wrapper('3110'); return false;\" title=\"Blahp doesn't build with Globus 5.2\">#3110</a></span></td>\n<td align=\"center\" valign=\"center\" width=\"30\">\n<span class=\"icon ptr1\">\u00a0</span></td>\n<td align=\"left\" valign=\"top\">\nBlahp doesn't build with Globus 5.2</td></tr>\n</tbody></table>", "attachments": "<html><head></head><body></body></html>", "check_ins": "<table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\n<tbody><tr><td align=\"right\" valign=\"top\" width=\"160\">2012-Jun-19 15:29</td>\n<td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" width=\"30\">\n<span class=\"icon dot\">\u00a0</span></td>\n<td align=\"left\" valign=\"top\"> \nCheck-in <span class=\"chng\"><a href=\"https://github.com/htcondor/htcondor/commit/3c417e180ff406d41d183081d2e1a41c5ad60f6f\">[32412]</a></span>: Ensure our libltdl can be found if not installed in /usr/lib. <span class=\"ticket\"><a class=\"resolved\" href=\"/wiki-archive/tickets/?ticket=2838\" onclick=\"get_ticket_and_populate_wrapper('2838'); return false;\" title=\"Update Globus external to 5.2.x\">#2838</a></span> Add libltdl.so to the link line so that the Condor binary's RUNPATH is used to find our copy of it if there's no system version installed.  (By Jaime Frey )</td></tr>\n<tr><td align=\"right\" valign=\"top\" width=\"160\">2012-Jun-12 14:55</td>\n<td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" width=\"30\">\n<span class=\"icon dot\">\u00a0</span></td>\n<td align=\"left\" valign=\"top\"> \nCheck-in <span class=\"chng\"><a href=\"https://github.com/htcondor/htcondor/commit/a14192c654a6d109a3069cab44ea49da7928f7e1\">[32284]</a></span>: Version history: Condor uses Globus 5.2.1. <span class=\"ticket\"><a class=\"resolved\" href=\"/wiki-archive/tickets/?ticket=2838\" onclick=\"get_ticket_and_populate_wrapper('2838'); return false;\" title=\"Update Globus external to 5.2.x\">#2838</a></span>  (By Jaime Frey )</td></tr>\n<tr><td align=\"right\" valign=\"top\" width=\"160\">2012-Jun-11 19:22</td>\n<td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" width=\"30\">\n<span class=\"icon dot\">\u00a0</span></td>\n<td align=\"left\" valign=\"top\"> \nCheck-in <span class=\"chng\"><a href=\"https://github.com/htcondor/htcondor/commit/926f809c466d3b4dcec22fc9e534aa4ebea2953f\">[32271]</a></span>: Include libltdl from build machine in UW packages. <span class=\"ticket\"><a class=\"resolved\" href=\"/wiki-archive/tickets/?ticket=2838\" onclick=\"get_ticket_and_populate_wrapper('2838'); return false;\" title=\"Update Globus external to 5.2.x\">#2838</a></span> Globus 5.2.1 depends on the system libltdl by default. This library isn't included in a base installation of many flavors of linux. Therefore, we should include it in the tarball distribution of Condor.  (By Jaime Frey )</td></tr>\n<tr><td align=\"right\" valign=\"top\" width=\"160\">2012-May-03 12:07</td>\n<td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" width=\"30\">\n<span class=\"icon dot\">\u00a0</span></td>\n<td align=\"left\" valign=\"top\"> \nCheck-in <span class=\"chng\"><a href=\"https://github.com/htcondor/htcondor/commit/f1b54f6bedf223e3c15caa82e9c70d654e196fdb\">[31915]</a></span>: Update Globus external to 5.2.1. <span class=\"ticket\"><a class=\"resolved\" href=\"/wiki-archive/tickets/?ticket=2838\" onclick=\"get_ticket_and_populate_wrapper('2838'); return false;\" title=\"Update Globus external to 5.2.x\">#2838</a></span> Even now that we dynamically link against Globus libraries, we continue to have trouble with the Globus external when globus_xio tries to dlopen() its plugins. dlopen() doesn't find libraries if LD_LIBRARY_PATH isn't set.  (By Jaime Frey )</td></tr>\n</tbody></table>", "type": "enhance", "last_change": "2012-Jun-12 14:56", "status": "resolved", "created": "2012-Feb-21 13:54", "fixed_version": "2012-Feb-21 13:54", "broken_version": "v070700", "priority": "4", "subsystem": "Libs", "assigned_to": "jfrey", "derived_from": "", "creator": "jfrey", "rust": "", "customer_group": "other", "visibility": "public", "notify": "", "due_date": ""}